Computers are, at their core, incredibly dumb; a transistor, billions of wh=
ich lie at the heart of the fastest chips in the world, are simple on-off s=
witches, the state of which is represented by a 1 or a 0. What makes them u=
seful is that they are dumb at incomprehensible speed; the Apple A16 in the=
